== Welcome to redport

New Features
* full security support
* friendly error page 
* performance and caching
* photo display shuffling 
* implement fancy box
* select feature display
* thumbnail generator tool

v1.2
* add captcha
* replace lightbox with fancybox
* feedback will be moved in-page
* performance and caching
* implement seadragon
* transfer photo management to local db
* add simple login

v1.1
* refresh administration tool
* analytics
* feedback page
* simple admin for viewing feedbacks
* featured photo
* showing of titles

v1.0
* customizable css
* integrated with flickr
* uses lightbox for viewing

HOW TO USE
* copy and modify

configurations
  - database.template => database.yml
  - config.template => config.yml
  - flickr.template => flickr.yml

shared views
  - _about.html.template => _about.html.erb
  - _analytics.html.template => _analytics.html.erb
  
* run
  - rake db:migrate
  - rake gems:install
